Using left most digit as the sign bit, 1 means negative.

one's complemennt: flip every digit

two's complement: flip every digit then plus 1
1000    -8  // min of 4 bit integers
1001    -7
1010    -6
1011    -5
1100    -4
1101    -3
1110    -2
1111    -1
0000    0
0001    1
0010    2
0011    3
0100    4
0101    5
0110    6
0111    7   // max of 4 bit integers since the left most bit is the sign bit 
